'''Chrysozephyrus''' is a [[butterfly]] [[genus]] in the [[family (biology)|family]] [[Lycaenidae]]. They were formerly included in ''[[Thecla (genus)|Thecla]]''.

===Selected species===
* ''[[Chrysozephyrus ataxus]]'' &ndash; [[Wonderful Hairstreak]]
** ''Chrysozephyrus ataxus lingi'' <small>Okano & Okura, 1969</small>
* ''[[Chrysozephyrus birupa]]'' &ndash; [[Fawn Hairstreak]]
* ''[[Chrysozephyrus disparatus]]''
** ''Chrysozephyrus disparatus pseudotaiwanus'' <small>(Howarth, 1957)</small>
* ''[[Chrysozephyrus duma]]'' &ndash; [[Metallic Green Hairstreak]]
* ''[[Chrysozephyrus esakii]]'' <small>(Sonan, 1940)</small>
* ''[[Chrysozephyrus jakamensis]]'' &ndash; [[Jakama Hairstreak]]
* ''[[Chrysozephyrus kabrua]]'' &ndash; [[Kabru Hairstreak]]
** ''Chrysozephyrus kabrua niitakanus'' <small>(Kano, 1928)</small>
* ''[[Chrysozephyrus khasia]]'' &ndash; [[Tailless Metallic Green Hairstreak]]
* ''[[Chrysozephyrus kirbariensis]]'' &ndash; [[Kirbari Hairstreak]]
* ''[[Chrysozephyrus mushaellus]]'' <small>(Matsumura, 1938)</small>
* ''[[Chrysozephyrus nishikaze]]'' <small>(Araki & Sibatani, 1886)</small>
* ''[[Chrysozephyrus paona]]'' &ndash; [[Paona Hairstreak]]
* ''[[Chrysozephyrus rarasanus]]'' <small>(Matsumura, 1939)</small>
* ''[[Chrysozephyrus smaragdinus]]''<!-- ZoolSci22:989 -->
* ''[[Chrysozephyrus splendidulus]]'' <small>Murayama, 1965</small>
* ''[[Chrysozephyrus surioia]]'' &ndash; [[Cerulean Hairstreak]]
* ''[[Chrysozephyrus syla]]'' &ndash; [[Silver Hairstreak]]
* ''[[Chrysozephyrus vittata]]'' &ndash; [[Tytler's Hairstreak]]
* ''[[Chrysozephyrus yuchingkinus]]'' <small>Murayama & Shimonoya, 1965</small>
* ''[[Chrysozephyrus zoa]]'' &ndash; [[Powdered Green Hairstreak]]


